<emphasis id="B922EA82FFA2FFA5F8F0FAAAFE8F5C26" bold="true" box="[151,260,1291,1316]" pageId="11" pageNumber="570">PLATE 3.</emphasis>
Male holotype 
<taxonomicName id="4C564D13FFA2FFA5F9CFFAAAFDE55C21" authority="Penado &amp; Smit &amp; Aguiar &amp; Cravo &amp; Rego &amp; Santos &amp; Boieiro, 2020" authorityName="Penado &amp; Smit &amp; Aguiar &amp; Cravo &amp; Rego &amp; Santos &amp; Boieiro" authorityYear="2020" box="[424,622,1291,1315]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Oedosphenella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="570" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bob" status="sp. n.">
